notes.text: We've optimized how data is fetched when an object page is displayed
We now ensure that the links are correctly displayed on the quick view popover, when a dynamic semantic object is used
We now correctly request the count of all visible tabs on the ListReport
You can now configure the x-axis of a chart as the time axis in the content area of an analytical list page
You can now use SAP Fiori tools in adaptation projects to adapt the list report
Applications can now disable the history of recently entered values for certain fields
We now ensure the handling of NavigationRestriction is in line with the protocol
We no longer show an error message in the console when the filter bar is hidden
